661
00:58:58,600 --> 00:59:00,470
Komorník Fu.

662
00:59:02,360 --> 00:59:05,150
Prepáčte.

663
00:59:05,150 --> 00:59:10,030
Madam mi prikázala sa vrátiť k nej a Tian Ji.

664
00:59:10,030 --> 00:59:12,760
To je v poriadku.

665
00:59:12,760 --> 00:59:14,580
No tak, usmej sa.

666
00:59:14,580 --> 00:59:19,110
